Interface PsiDirectory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iconable, Navigatable, NavigatablePsiElement, NavigationItem, PsiCheckedRenameElement, PsiElement, PsiFileSystemItem, PsiNamedElement, UserDataHolder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PsiDirectoryImpl, PsiJavaDirectoryImpl

    public interface PsiDirectory
extends PsiFileSystemItem
    Represents a file system directory and allows to access its contents.
